  "text": "For this purpose we will first mimic isothermal rebreathing as it has been carried out by various investigators [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . More precisely, rebreathing was instituted after t start = 2 min of free tidal breathing at rest by inhaling to total lung capacity and exhaling until the bag was filled, thereby providing an initial bag concentration which can be assumed to resemble the normal end-exhaled level, i.e.,",
